{"tid":137542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦塔橋蘇州有山寨版　網民嘲醜出國際","createTime":"2017-02-28T01:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T05:29:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e24cd3a42a9e8a7f0b5da7cededd33daa2586b1","tid":137542,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:43:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>倫敦塔橋蘇州有山寨版　網民嘲醜出國際<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/bkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2Fbkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001.html&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9ff23397\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/bkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001.html</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/photo/bkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_01p.jpg&h=49c9d77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江蘇蘇州有山寨版倫敦塔橋，遭網民狠批「東施效顰」。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n中國山寨建築眾多，世界著名旅遊景點英國倫敦塔橋，在中國也有山寨版。江蘇蘇州近年有人建造了山寨倫敦塔橋，規模上更比原版大一倍，橋上塔樓從兩座變成四座，看上去相當宏偉，但網民紛紛批評「東施效顰」、「醜出國際」。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/photo/bkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_03p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_03p.jpg&h=673ffffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四座塔樓各高40米。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n這座塔橋位於蘇州相城區華元路，外形參照倫敦塔橋建造，但橋面比原橋更寬廣，塔樓數量亦多出兩座。據資料顯示，大橋橫向分為快線、慢線和行人路，總寬近46米；而塔樓下部則供非機動車通行。四座塔樓各高40米，塔樓之間設有懸空行人通道，供行人觀光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/photo/bkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_02p.jpg&h=7044ebbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山寨倫敦塔橋有四座塔樓。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n山寨塔橋外形算宏偉，但中國網民都不欣賞，稱「國外的月亮不一定都比中國圓啊」、「這給我的感覺完全是畫虎不成反類犬」、「這東施效顰，簡直是醜出國際」。另有人指蘇州整體江南古園林城市風格，與大橋格格不入，「中國一直模仿外國，卻不能超越人家」；亦有人笑稱「終於能假裝自己去過倫敦了！」「杭州還有埃菲爾鐵塔呢！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/photo/bkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170227101158822-0227_05011_001_05p.jpg&h=14258676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國倫敦塔橋是世界知名旅遊景點。（網上資料圖片）"},{"pid":"e7ad58f2fd6c1c9ed8d38975a9f27d3db1ab8029","tid":137542,"uid":86255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:46:10.000Z","msg":"屌那星"},{"pid":"ee0d0f7b68340f24ad383cb2932a69541ca05d65","tid":137542,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b33c99d7bf3095c420a00e27ee3d855a4d7341","tid":137542,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:09:14.000Z","msg":"超英趕美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b066bc1aae6b5cc24e1086632afdc673f9c469","tid":137542,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:11:32.000Z","msg":"做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a6062f715e7600e40539dbf55ce37b5f9e3371","tid":137542,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:11:34.000Z","msg":"好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾時整埋自由神像"},{"pid":"a548794192a1c4a70324f78a70769728600b4ed4","tid":137542,"uid":61232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T